snippet.title: Ultimate Custom Night - Mobile Update 04/14/2023
snippet.description:
We have taken alot of your input and intergrated it into this the next mobile update to Ultimate Custom Night including a revamped UI to make gameplay more manageable on a touchscreen device. Special shoutout to djsterf who's videos where of great help!

iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ultimate-custom-night/id1499849161

Google Play:https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.clickteam.ultimatecustomnight&hl=en_US&gl=US

Check out the change log below (Version 1.0.4 for Android & Version 1.0.3 for iOS)

- Revamped and improved user interface
- Player defined AI is now saved
- Subtitles in 11 languages (see app description)
- Resampled graphics at a higher resolution
- Improved audio support
- Revamped vibrations
- Various fixes and improvements

https://www.youtube.com/@djsterf
https://twitter.com/djsterf

#FNaF #Clickteam #Horror
